  "decision_conditions": [
    "Condition : 1 - This consent is for a limited period and shall expire on 01/09/2025 and the advertisement hereby approved shall be removed and the land reinstated to its former condition by that date. \r\nReason: The advertisement is only acceptable for a limited period, having regard to the amenity of the area in accordance with  policy LP9 of the Local Plan and the requirements of paragraph 141 of the National Planning Policy Framework.",
    "Condition : 2 - The development shall be carried out in accordance with the reports, specifications and drawings detailed PY4626/004, PY4626/005, PY4626/007\r\nReason: To ensure a satisfactory standard of development and to allow the local planning authority to review any potential changes to the scheme. \r\n",
    "Condition : 3 - The maximum steady brightness of the projecting sign hereby permitted is not to exceed 400 candelas per sq.m. \r\nReason: To ensure the proposed sign does not have an adverse effect on the amenity of the area in accordance with Council policy LP9 of the Local Plan and to comply with paragraph 141 of the National Planning Policy Framework.",
    "Condition : 4 - The illumination of the sign(s) hereby permitted shall be by static illumination only. \r\nReason: In the interest of highway safety and of the visual amenities of the locality in accordance with Council policy LP9 of the Local Plan and to comply with paragraph 141 of the National Planning Policy Framework.\r\n"
